 Klin is a console interface for Atcore. 
 
 usage :> kiln -d /dev/ttyUSB0 -p ~/file.gcode 
 
 switches: 

 -d <device>
    the device to connect to

 -b <baud> 
    baud to use; optional default baud is 112500
 
 -p <gcode>
    gcode file to print. 
    
